Class ConnectorConnPoolProbeProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.enterprise.resource.pool.monitor.ConnectionPoolProbeProvider
      • com.sun.enterprise.resource.pool.monitor.ConnectorConnPoolProbeProvider

  • public class ConnectorConnPoolProbeProvider
extends ConnectionPoolProbeProvider
    Probe provider interface for Connector connection pool related events to provide information related to the various objects on jca pool monitoring.
